response.overview: On April 6th GCW faces off TJPW live on TrillerTV+ straight from Penns Landing Caterers in Philadelphia, PA.  The TJPW team pro wrestling stars to take part are Miyu Yamashita, Yuki Aino, Shoko Nakajima, Rika Tatsumi, Mizuki, Maki Itoh, Miu Watanabe, Yuki Kamifuku, Hyper Misao, Nao Kakuta, Raku, Pom, Harajuku, Suzume and Arisu Endo.  The GCW team pro wrestling stars to take part are Masha Slamovich, Rina Yamashita, Steph De Lander, Dark Sheik, Billie Starkz, Sawyer Wreck, Janai Kai, Allie Katch, Shazza McKenzie, Session Moth Martina.  Tune in for this exciting wrestling showdown, packed with jaw-dropping stunts and unbridled energy!  *lineup subject to change
response.title: GCW vs TJPW
